  m_text: 'Welcome to the VR Hand Rehabilitation System.


    This application guides
    you through therapeutic hand exercises using real-time hand tracking on your
    Meta Quest headset.


    <b>Features</b>

    - 5 guided exercises with adaptive
    difficulty

    - Real-time finger tracking and grip analysis

    - Audio coaching
    and visual feedback

    - Session progress saved to your profile


    <b>How
    to Begin</b>

    Look to your right and enter your User ID on the session panel,
    then press Begin Session.'
